{
  "texts": [
    "Conduct imaging studies, such as CT scans or MRI, to assess the extent of the tumor.",
    "Consultation with specialists: multidisciplinary team, including oral and maxillofacial surgeons, medical oncologists, radiation oncologists, and dental professionals.",
    "Treatment modalities: surgery, radiation therapy, and chemotherapy.",
    "The choice depends on the stage, location, and extent of the tumor.",
    "Dental evaluation and care: address dental issues, such as extraction of non-restorable teeth, before initiating treatment."
  ]
}